HEADWORD: Soliform
<hw>Sol"i*form</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>sol</ets>
sun + <ets>-form</ets>.]</ety> <def>Like the sun in form, appearance, or
nature; resembling the sun.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
